text.tspan: The openSUSE project is a community program sponsored by Novell.

flowRoot.flowPara: openSUSE is a free Linux-based operating system for your desktop or laptop computer. You can surf the web, manage your e-mails and photos, do office work, play videos or music.
This bootable CD allows you to try openSUSE without installing it. No change is made to the existing system unless you explicitly chose to install.
